plot: Khloe and Kourtney have a copy of Kim's Vogue cover blown up and framed to show they care about their sister's big accomplishment. Then, Khloe and Kourtney shop 'till they drop to fill Khloe's new home, but will Kourtney's surprise decorating bill ruin the vibe--and their Miami mini va-cay? Plus, see Bruce Jenner's reaction when he catches Kris and her mom testing out M.J's magical gummy bears. Heads will roll!—Anonymous
